race.comment: BRAZEN DIVA (2) returns from a spell and has been in money four of her five starts. The speedy mare placed here at her only fresh run and comes to this with two Cranbourne jumpout wins under the saddle. Rates best. UYUNI (8) ran well on debut to finish second over 1103m at Kyneton in a tougher race. Will benefit from that experience, and this is winnable with the extra fitness. REGINA D'ORO (4) has raced just once and that was back in July last year but has been readied with a series of nice efforts at the jumpouts. OUR SQUAMOSA (6) is a filly by Squamosa making her first appearance. Has recorded a win and a second in the last two jump-outs. Trained on the course so keep safe along with ZOOM QUEEN (11) who is speedy and gets blinkers on so could improve at start number two.
